import React from 'react';
import {
  Card, CardImg, CardText, CardBody,
  CardTitle, CardSubtitle, Button
} from 'reactstrap';
import { Container, Row, Col } from 'reactstrap';

const Boxes = (props) => {
  return (
    <Row xs="4">

        <Col><Card style={{marginTop: '8%', width:'20%'}}>
        <CardImg 
        top 
        className="img-fluid"  
        src="static/images/4.png" 
        alt="Card image cap" />

        <CardBody>
          <CardTitle>Card title</CardTitle>
          <CardSubtitle>Card subtitle</CardSubtitle>
          <CardText>Some quick example text.</CardText>
          <Button>Button</Button>
        </CardBody>
      </Card>
</Col>
        <Col>     

    
     
<Card className="xs=4" style={{marginTop: '8%', width:'20%'}}>
<CardImg 
top 
className="img-fluid"  
src="static/images/4.png" 
alt="Card image cap" />

<CardBody>
  <CardTitle>Card title</CardTitle>
  <CardSubtitle>Card subtitle</CardSubtitle>
  <CardText>Some quick example text.</CardText>
  <Button>Button</Button>
</CardBody>
</Card>
</Col>
        <Col><Card style={{marginTop: '8%', width:'20%'}}>
        <CardImg 
        top 
        className="img-fluid"  
        src="static/images/4.png" 
        alt="Card image cap" />

        <CardBody>
          <CardTitle>Card title</CardTitle>
          <CardSubtitle>Card subtitle</CardSubtitle>
          <CardText>Some quick example text.</CardText>
          <Button>Button</Button>
        </CardBody>
      </Card></Col>
        <Col>Column</Col>
      </Row>
  );
};

export default Boxes;
